04:23.962 --> 04:29.630
But he wrote those memoirs 30 or 40 years later, and his memory was at 4.

04:29.991 --> 04:33.977
He didn't write them 40 years later because he was dead 40 years later.

04:33.997 --> 04:34.578
30 years later.

04:35.920 --> 04:37.662
And his memory was at 4.

04:38.323 --> 04:46.555
