24:11.028 --> 24:13.971
And the first books were delivered to him on December 17.

24:18.675 --> 24:21.438
And the first printing consisted of 6,000 copies.

24:24.560 --> 24:26.582
So there were four plates that had to be hand-colored.

24:26.602 --> 24:29.205
